[We seem to have further clarification on the issue of which type of banana
wilt -- fungal or bacterial -- is causing the recent concerns in East
Africa (see previous posts listed below). Putting a plant pathology problem
into a social context, this story shows the importance and difficulties of
agricultural liaison work.
